    "body": "## Problem\r\nCurrently the `:lua {code}` and `:luafile` commands do not expose the selected range in the buffer when the code was executed. I.e. when making a selection in visual mode, and then invoking either `:lua {code}` or `:luafile`, the executed lua snippet should be able to determine the selected range.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nIntroduce a local lua object `ev` that contains `firstline` and `lastline`, and make that available to the executed lua snippet. This object can contain more fields in the future if necessary.\r\n\r\ncloses #7177 ",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-10T22:42:26Z",
